                     <interp inst="t18000528-14-off79" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18000528-14-cd80" type="crimeDate">4th of November</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18000528-14-off79 t18000528-14-cd80"></join>, a great-coat, value 2l. a pair of buckles, value 12s. and a silver tea-spoon, value 1s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18000528-14-victim202" type="victimName">
                           William 
